{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 NEW BIBLE STUDY:}{\plain \fs24 \f8   Is there evidence in the world around us that should be apparent to all that God exists?   Or \softline
is belief that God exists purely a "leap of faith"?   Does the existence of God conflict with modern day science?  \softline
Or does even modern day science have discoveries that support the existence of God?   Is the existence of God \softline
completely divorced from reason and rational thinking?  Or are there reasonable and logic perspectives that are \softline
compatible with God's existence?  Let's explore these questions and many others during a five week Adult Sunday \softline
School series called "Natural Theology".  As Paul states in 2 Corinthians 10:5, "We demolish arguments and every \softline
pretension that sets itself up against the knowledge of God, and we take captive every thought and make it \softline
obedient to Christ." We meet in Klein Hall every Sunday at 9:50 am, facilitated by Jason Tolbert.\par
}{\plain \fs24 \f8 \par
}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 Thrivent Choice Dollars}{\plain \fs24 \f8  - Are you looking for an easy and simple way to supplement your financial support to \softline
Living Savior? For Thrivent members, please consider using your Thrivent Choice Dollars and direct those dollars \softline
to Living Savior. Thrivent Choice lets eligible Thrivent members distribute outreach funds to churches and \softline
nonprofit organizations. The amount available for an individual member to direct varies based upon insurance \softline
premiums and contract value. The process is straight forward: (1) Visit Thrivent.com/thriventchoice, (2) In the "get \softline
started" section, click on Direct Thrivent Choice Dollars, (3) Login and follow the steps. If you have a problem, call \softline
800-847-4836 and say "Thrivent Choice" or contact your Thrivent representative. The amount available from 2019 \softline
that you can direct is available until the end of March 2020. Please consider designating your dollars to Living \softline
Savior.\par
