}{\plain \fs24 \b\f8 Please Help the LSLC Puerto Rico Relief Project: }{\plain \fs24 \f8  In the wake of recent earthquake and continuing recovery from \softline
hurricane Maria, we are supporting relief efforts on the ground (Miguel Quinones).  We are working with \softline
Ambiente de Gracia congregation to maximize our impact. To date we have shipped 2 cases of repellent and two \softline
2-room tents, provided funding for 8 mattresses, cases of diapers and cases of infant formula.  A list of requested \softline
items is in the Narthex.  If you would prefer to make a monetary donation, please make your check out to LSLC \softline
and indicate Puerto Rico Relief on the check. Please see Miki Kolton or Marie Acevedo for more information.  \par
